"""
Snakemake file for downstream analysis of 2M downsampled samples.

load modules:

    ml bioinfo-tools snakemake

sbatch command:
    
    sbatch -A ngi2016004 -J contam -n 12 -p core -t 1-00:00:00 --wrap "snakemake -p -j 12 --use-singularity -k --rerun-incomplete" --mail-user phojer@kth.se --mail-type ALL
"""

